</ul>
<p><a name="Vector_calculus" id="Vector_calculus"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Electromagnetic_wave_equation&amp;action=edit&amp;section=28" title="Edit section: Vector calculus">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Vector calculus</span></h3>
