<p><a name="Biographies" id="Biographies"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Electromagnetic_wave_equation&amp;action=edit&amp;section=29" title="Edit section: Biographies">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Biographies</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Andre_Marie_Ampere" title="Andre Marie Ampere" class="mw-redirect">Andre Marie Ampere</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Albert_Einstein" title="Albert Einstein">Albert Einstein</a></li>
